dcterms:description: A corpus containing sentences of the form 'The [NOUN1] [PREPOSITION] the [NOUN2] [is/are] [ADJECTIVE].' It is used to study the embeddings of verbs in relation to their subjects and non-argument nouns.
dcterms:title: Prepositional Phrase Corpus

dcterms:description: A corpus containing sentences of the form 'The [NOUN1] that [VERB] the [NOUN2] [is/are] [ADJECTIVE].' It is used to analyze the embeddings of verbs in relation to their subjects and non-argument nouns.
dcterms:title: Relative Clause Corpus

dcterms:creator: Jeffrey Pennington
Richard Socher
Christopher D Manning
dcterms:description: GloVe embeddings are global vectors for word representation, used to create hypothesis models for analyzing the representational geometry of contextualized embeddings.
dcterms:title: GloVe embeddings

dcterms:creator: Jacob Devlin
Ming-Wei Chang
Kenton Lee
Kristina Toutanova
dcterms:description: BERT embeddings are contextualized word representations used to analyze linguistic dependencies in the study.
dcterms:title: BERT embeddings

dcterms:description: A corpus containing sentences that include reflexive pronouns, used to study the relationship between pronouns and their antecedents.
dcterms:title: Reflexive Corpus

dcterms:description: A corpus containing sentences that include pronominal references, used to study the relationship between pronouns and their antecedents.
dcterms:title: Pronominal Corpus

dcterms:description: A corpus containing sentences that do not require a direct object, used to analyze the embeddings of verbs.
dcterms:title: Intransitive Corpus

dcterms:description: A corpus containing intransitive sentences with adjectives, used to analyze the embeddings of verbs.
dcterms:title: Intransitive + Adjective Corpus

dcterms:description: A corpus containing sentences that require a direct object, used to analyze the embeddings of verbs.
dcterms:title: Transitive Corpus

dcterms:description: A corpus containing transitive sentences with adjectives, used to analyze the embeddings of verbs.
dcterms:title: Transitive + Adjective Corpus
